AF/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>我现在想把站点搬走，想找个能免费部署的地方，要求是不能花钱，免费额度低点没事，于是这几天尝试了国内几乎所有支持免费静态托管的服务商，总结心得，遂成此文，分享给大家。</description></item><item><title>美化了一下站点</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Feb 2026 13:49:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>非常克制地美化了一下自己的站点。</description></item><item><title>基于Shortcodes的Hugo进阶使用——功能扩展与美观方向</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/hugo%E4%B8%8Emarkdown%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Feb 2026 03:38:38 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/hugo%E4%B8%8Emarkdown%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A82/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>Hugo 本身没有像 WordPress 那样“一键安装”的插件后台，但它通过几种非常硬核的方式实现了类似插件的功能。本文简单的记录一些常见的Shortcodes</description></item><item><title>基于FrontMatter的Hugo进阶使用——数据库方向</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/hugo%E4%B8%8Emarkdown%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Feb 2026 12:00:27 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/hugo%E4%B8%8Emarkdown%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>原来Hugo对Markdown的解析是如此美妙，原来Markdown文件是如此迷人。</description></item><item><title>还是使用docker折腾聚宽吧</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 18:02:52 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>聚宽是个大坑，对库版本要求太严格，怎么改都不行，只好用docker来解决了。</description></item><item><title>学习使用聚宽</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BDing/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 13:21:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BDing/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>聚宽提供了比较少见的可以免费用一段时间的量化数据集，尤其是可转债数据，聚宽给得比较大方。我先尝试使用一下。</description></item><item><title>jupyter服务器更新了，小玩具绽放第二春</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E6%96%B0jupyter%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E6%96%B0jupyter%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>再次折腾！这次不仅更换了jupyter服务器，还连上公网了，也算吃顿好了.</description></item><item><title>可转债研究宝典</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%8F%AF%E8%BD%AC%E5%80%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 25 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%8F%AF%E8%BD%AC%E5%80%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一篇很好的可转债教程，算是我的入门教材，面对现在大牛市的行情，这个教程有点不合时宜了，但是温故知新。常看常新。我稍微修订了一下，改了下格式和行文，发在这里。
可转债的核心就是&lt;strong&gt;三要素&lt;/strong&gt;，做可转债的核心就是&lt;strong&gt;三知道&lt;/strong&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item><item><title>国内可用的docker镜像站点</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84docker%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84docker%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>&lt;p&gt;最近在折腾服务器，Docker Hub官方仓库经常连不上，拉取超时、报错 &lt;code&gt;i/o timeout&lt;/code&gt; 等问题，我搜集了一下国内可用的地址，截至2026 年 1 月最新实测可用。这里留一份备查。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Rsync使用笔记</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/rsync%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/rsync%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="-前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;📖 前言&lt;/span&gt;
